description.post_condition: Recover the config file by command: mv /etc/ambd/config-bak /etc/ambd/config and restart ambd process(i.e. kill -9 159;ambd -D).

step.step_desc: Make a copy of origin ambd config file:cp /etc/ambd/config /etc/ambd/config-bak
Make AMB database sink to be installed an enabled for testing: cp /etc/ambd/examples/databaseconfig /etc/ambd/config
Restart the ambd process(i.e. kill -9 'pid of ambd'; ambd -D )
